---
// WhoWeAre.astro - Premium "Quem Somos" Section
---

<section id="quem-somos" class="who-we-are">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-layout">
      <!-- Left Column: Content -->
      <div class="content-side">
        <span class="super-headline">CONHEÇA A NOSSA HISTÓRIA</span>
        <h2 class="main-title">Canalizadores de <span>Confiança</span> Perto de si.</h2>
        <p class="history-text">
          Os nossos canalizadores são dos profissionais mais reconhecidos no mercado Português, porque estamos comprometidos com um serviço fabuloso à mais de 15 anos, oferecendo serviços de canalização, desentupimentos e limpezas de fossas, a um custo acessível (low cost) a qualquer um. 
        </p>
        <p class="history-text">
          Trabalhamos com qualquer tipo de cliente, desde particulares, comerciais ou até mesmo industriais. Na Top Canalizadores trabalhamos para superar as suas expectativas todos os dias!
        </p>
        <div class="cta-area">
          <p class="cta-msg">Ligue 24/7 para o nosso serviço de emergência!</p>
          <a href="tel:+351969146836" class="btn-primary">PEÇA JÁ O SEU ORÇAMENTO</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Image & Feature -->
      <div class="image-side">
        <div class="image-wrapper" style="position: relative; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); height: 100%;">
          <img src="/images/hero-desentupimentos.png" alt="Profissionais Top Canalizador" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
          <div class="image-overlay" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(12, 28, 44, 0.95), transparent); padding: 40px 30px 30px;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #51acfb;">Sempre Prontos a Ajudar</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); line-height: 1.5;">Piquete de intervenção rápida 24H em toda a região.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .who-we-are {
    padding: 100px 20px;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: #252525;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .grid-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .super-headline {
    color: #51acfb;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .main-title {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    color: #0c1c2c;
  }

  .main-title span {
    color: #51acfb;
  }

  .history-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-area {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 30px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-left: 5px solid #51acfb;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .cta-msg {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #0c1c2c;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #ef4c37;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 16px 35px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(239, 76, 55, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #d84432;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(239, 76, 55, 0.4);
  }

  .info-card {
    background: #0c1c2c;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .card-header h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #51acfb;
  }

  .card-header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 35px;
  }

  .progress-bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 25px;
  }

  .skill-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .progress-bg {
    height: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #51acfb, #2d94ee);
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: width 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .bottom-features {
    margin-top: 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 30px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .feature-tag {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #0c1c2c;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .grid-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 50px;
    }
    .who-we-are {
      padding: 70px 20px;
    }
    .main-title {
      font-size: 34px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bottom-features {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
